  "texts": [
    "Moreover, most joint-design schemes involve the non-convex optimization algorithms, which hinders their online implementation.However, these three ISAC schemes often face the challenge of high computational complexity due to balancing the two functionalities, posing a barrier to their widespread adoption.",
    "This motivates researchers to develop low-complexity algorithms for practical use.",
    "Fortunately, artificial intelligence (AI), including machine learning (ML) [55], deep learning (DL) [56], deep reinforcement learning (DRL) [57,58], and federated learning (FL) [59][60][61], has achieved remarkable success in various fields such as computer vision (CV), natural language processing (NLP), and autonomous driving.",
    "These techniques demonstrate the powerful capabilities of automatic feature extraction, nonlinear fitting, and decision making.",
    "Motivated by these advances, AI can deal with the challenging tasks of wireless communication, such as modulation detection [62,63] and channel estimation [64,65]."
  ]
}